    "description": "<p>\r\n\tFormerly know as Alfred Wong Partnership, AWP Pte Ltd was Founded in 1957 by the first Singapore Institute of Architects Gold Medalist.  AWP remains committed to excellence in design and delivery through innovation , appropriate methodology and experience.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tAWP is listed Panel 1 on the Public Sector Panels of Consultants and received ISO:9001, ISO:14001 and ISO:18001 in recognition of the quality of its management , design for safety and ongoing commitment to environmental management and sustainable design.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tWith principal offices in Singapore and China and  associate  offices  in the UK, Asia and Australia, AWP can undertake both Regional and  International projects and has successfully completed commissions in China, India, Indonesia, Malaysia, Middle-East, North Africa, Philippines, Singapore, Sri Lanka, Thailand and Vietnam.</p>\r\n",
